lead_paragraph: Tom Brady got one practice in last week before facing the New York Jets. The New England Patriots hope his ailing knee allows him to get a few more in this week before hosting the Los Angeles Rams next Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Banged-Up Brady Glad Week's Over _ and With Win for Patriots
